---
title: NerGuard Inference Pipeline
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User
    participant PIITester
    participant Model as mDeBERTa-v3
    participant Uncertainty as Uncertainty Module
    participant Router as Entity Router
    participant LLM as LLM Backend

    User->>PIITester: analyze_text(text)
    activate PIITester

    Note over PIITester: Tokenize + Sliding Window<br/>(512 tokens, stride 382)

    PIITester->>Model: forward(input_ids)
    activate Model
    Model-->>PIITester: logits [batch, seq, 43]
    deactivate Model

    PIITester->>Uncertainty: compute_entropy_confidence(logits)
    activate Uncertainty
    Note over Uncertainty: H = entropy(softmax(z))<br/>c = max(softmax(z))
    Uncertainty-->>PIITester: entropy[], confidence[], pred_ids[]
    deactivate Uncertainty

    loop For each token
        alt Confident (H ≤ 0.583 or c ≥ 0.787)
            PIITester->>PIITester: Use model prediction
        else Uncertain + Routable Entity
            PIITester->>Router: should_route(label, entropy, confidence)
            activate Router

            alt Blocked (GIVENNAME, SURNAME, I-tokens)
                Router-->>PIITester: False
            else Routable (CREDITCARD, TELEPHONE, etc.)
                Router-->>PIITester: True
                deactivate Router

                PIITester->>LLM: disambiguate(token, context)
                activate LLM
                Note over LLM: gpt-4o-mini<br/>Context: ±400 chars
                LLM-->>PIITester: corrected_label
                deactivate LLM
            end
        end
    end

    PIITester-->>User: List[TokenResult]
    deactivate PIITester
